eu.planets_project.TB.interfaces.data.model
Interface Experiment

All Superinterfaces:
ExperimentPhase
public interface Experiment
extends ExperimentPhase

-Phases: Every Experiment consists out of four phases Setup, Approval, Execution and Analysis Every Phase may consist itself of multiple steps (e.g. setup experiment includes: fill in basic properties, design a workflow, etc.). Within this steps it's possible to navigate forward and backward - afer a phase has completed its data may not be modified any longer.

- Status: Every phase contains a status as well as there's an overall status status for the entire Experiment
